### Health
GET http://localhost:3000/health

### List agents
GET http://localhost:3000/agents

### Create agent
POST http://localhost:3000/agents
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Sales Agent",
  "provider": "OpenAI",
  "model": "gpt-5"
}

### Issue token
POST http://localhost:3000/tokens/issue
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "principal": "user:chinmay",
  "agent": "agent:research_assistant",
  "scopes": ["search.web"]
}
